reviewText: Not Mazinger, Mech Baron is adapted in the 80s like Mazinger The movie with real actors, this was released in several cinemas in the world with great success in South America in cinemas and on video, as 25 years ago was looking and my dream has come true, I recommend it for fans of the genre and assure a good time with friends, the movie is spoken in Spanish, if you want to understand perfectly, you should understand a Spanish minimum.
